    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        h2.section-heading Services
        h3.section-subheading.text-muted What can I offer?
    .row.text-center
      .col-md-4
        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          i.fa.fa-code-fork.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
