        p
          | With websites becoming increasingly complex and often integrating
          | live or personalised data, it is essential to ensure your
          | <i>application</i> can both convey your offering and engage your 
          | visitors. With an understanding how a site can communicate with 
          | other services and how best to use these, I can help you to create 
          | a truly interactive experience for your users.
        p
          | I am a big fan of the MEAN Javascript stack and am constantly 
          | striving to learn new technologies in order to stay at
          | the forefront of an evolving sector. This ensures that I always
          | choose the best tool for the job, and has also inspired some 
          | personal creative projects.
