        p
          | Having a fantastic interactive web application is great, but if it
          | doesn't look good then nobody will want to stay for long. With an 
          | eye for detail*, as well as technologies such as Bootstrap, HTML5
          | and CSS3, I will make sure that your application not only does the
          | job, but looks great too.
        p.text-muted
          | * and a reputation for pixel counting!
      .col-md-4
        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          i.fa.fa-graduation-cap.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        h4.service-heading Consultancy
        p
          | As someone who enjoys learning new skills and technologies, I am 
          | also keen to share this knowledge with others. My experience of
          | training and mentoring others in a professional capacity has also 
          | led me to volunteer with Enrych Berkshire to teach people with 
          | disabilities new skills.
          
